Hardware TestAndSet Logic:
```c
bool TestAndSet(bool *target) {
  bool rv = *target;
  *target = true;
  return rv;
}
```
Usage:
```c
while (TestAndSet(&lock)) { /* do nothing */ }
// Critical Section
lock = false;
```

content.algorithm_steps:
Wait (P / Down):
```c
wait(S) {
  while (S <= 0) ; // busy wait or sleep
  S--;
}
```
Signal (V / Up):
```c
signal(S) {
  S++;
}
```
